WEBVTT


00:00:18.940 --> 00:00:23.880
♪Only after bloom comes fruit♪

00:00:25.290 --> 00:00:29.260
♪Who says glory must fade to the past♪

00:00:31.920 --> 00:00:37.010
♪Only through thunder
do you reach the clouds♪

00:00:38.210 --> 00:00:43.120
♪Who made you the crown of every peak♪

00:00:44.650 --> 00:00:47.930
♪I stand at the center of the stage♪

00:00:47.930 --> 00:00:51.000
♪My shadow is pinned against the wall♪

00:00:51.710 --> 00:00:56.660
♪Facing the light earns every medal♪

00:00:57.700 --> 00:01:00.880
♪Little birds,
save your needless pecking♪

00:01:00.880 --> 00:01:04.160
♪The open sky rises high♪

00:01:04.700 --> 00:01:09.830
♪When night falls,
the moon begins to shine♪

00:01:10.600 --> 00:01:13.860
♪I stand in the heart of these lands♪

00:01:13.860 --> 00:01:17.220
♪My shadow bears no crown or robe♪

00:01:17.630 --> 00:01:23.300
♪Then I know truth needs no disguise♪

00:01:23.710 --> 00:01:26.960
♪The green hills see me as I am♪

00:01:26.960 --> 00:01:30.290
♪Like dew, lightning,
and moon on the river♪

00:01:30.690 --> 00:01:34.730
♪Showing me exactly who I am♪

00:01:34.730 --> 00:01:35.980
=The Lead=

00:01:36.020 --> 00:01:37.900
=Episode 26=

00:01:56.480 --> 00:01:57.960
There are three beds here.

00:01:57.960 --> 00:01:59.000
Where's the other guy?

00:01:59.550 --> 00:02:00.760
Just the two of us, Uncle.

00:02:12.670 --> 00:02:13.510
Get up.

00:02:13.960 --> 00:02:15.670
Sleep over there. I'm sleeping here.

00:02:15.840 --> 00:02:16.750
Why?

00:02:17.750 --> 00:02:19.390
Closer to the door. Easier for me.

00:02:27.430 --> 00:02:29.110
Are you glued to the bed?

00:02:59.480 --> 00:03:00.320
What are you doing?

00:03:00.760 --> 00:03:01.600
Brushing my teeth.

00:03:35.920 --> 00:03:36.760
What now?

00:03:38.120 --> 00:03:38.960
Taking a leak.

00:03:56.150 --> 00:03:57.870
I can't go with you watching me.

00:03:58.280 --> 00:04:00.030
What are you doing? Hurry up.

00:04:00.800 --> 00:04:02.470
I've been exhausted all day.

00:04:02.470 --> 00:04:03.680
Get to bed early.

00:04:24.400 --> 00:04:26.430
Why didn't he close the door?

00:04:46.030 --> 00:04:47.630
Thanks for today.

00:04:50.560 --> 00:04:51.710
It's just a tiny thing.

00:04:53.560 --> 00:04:54.400
Here's the deal.

00:04:55.520 --> 00:04:57.000
You're heading back tomorrow.

00:04:58.520 --> 00:05:00.240
Qin'e will report to her unit.

00:05:01.000 --> 00:05:02.590
Once the boss returns,

00:05:02.960 --> 00:05:05.400
she'll be busy with work and rehearsals.

00:05:05.870 --> 00:05:06.840
We won't have time for you.

00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:09.030
Just focus on your own things.

00:05:09.360 --> 00:05:10.200
Don't worry about me.

00:05:11.030 --> 00:05:11.870
Good night.

00:05:24.560 --> 00:05:26.280
I'm a light sleeper.

00:05:26.910 --> 00:05:28.120
Any little noise,

00:05:28.520 --> 00:05:29.710
and I wake right up.

00:05:30.840 --> 00:05:33.280
I can hear a pin drop.

00:05:40.910 --> 00:05:41.750
Uncle.

00:05:48.630 --> 00:05:49.470
Your face...

00:05:50.030 --> 00:05:51.710
Was it from an explosion?

00:05:54.160 --> 00:05:55.830
See? What did I tell you?

00:05:56.720 --> 00:05:59.600
I heard from a Laoshan Frontline comrade.

00:06:00.240 --> 00:06:01.430
He transported the wounded.

00:06:02.680 --> 00:06:03.520
What?

00:06:04.000 --> 00:06:04.840
You don't believe me?

00:06:07.270 --> 00:06:08.190
Let me tell you,

00:06:08.190 --> 00:06:09.270
people all say I

00:06:09.270 --> 00:06:12.510
only drove in the rear, not the front.

00:06:12.630 --> 00:06:13.470
But,

00:06:14.160 --> 00:06:15.830
he really went to the frontline.

00:06:16.390 --> 00:06:17.720
He saw those soldiers

00:06:17.720 --> 00:06:19.480
fighting to defend our home.

00:06:19.920 --> 00:06:21.000
No one backed down.

00:06:21.510 --> 00:06:23.920
Every single one risked their lives.

00:06:25.630 --> 00:06:26.470
So,

00:06:28.160 --> 00:06:29.040
as soon as I saw you,

00:06:30.000 --> 00:06:31.800
I felt a special connection.

00:06:32.160 --> 00:06:34.040
You are just like those people

00:06:34.040 --> 00:06:36.190
he described as burnt pitch-black.

00:06:36.190 --> 00:06:37.510
Exactly the same.

00:07:21.830 --> 00:07:23.360
This night was too long.

00:07:23.950 --> 00:07:26.120
Yi Qin'e couldn't sleep at all.

00:07:26.870 --> 00:07:29.360
Unable to sleep, she had to practice.

00:07:29.800 --> 00:07:31.270
She could only think of the past.

00:07:31.270 --> 00:07:32.830
Thinking of the County Troupe.

00:07:32.830 --> 00:07:34.630
Thinking of Feng Xiaoxiao.

00:07:36.120 --> 00:07:38.360
Yi Qin'e liked Feng Xiaoxiao.

00:07:39.270 --> 00:07:40.920
But Master Gou told her

00:07:40.920 --> 00:07:43.870
that actors shouldn't fall in love.

00:07:44.390 --> 00:07:45.230
If they do,

00:07:45.480 --> 00:07:46.950
the performance will suffer.

00:07:48.270 --> 00:07:50.120
She could only let her feelings

00:07:50.120 --> 00:07:51.120
sink deep down,

00:07:51.630 --> 00:07:53.040
into the dirt,

00:07:53.040 --> 00:07:54.720
and slowly fade away

00:07:54.720 --> 00:07:56.920
until they disappeared.

00:07:57.630 --> 00:08:02.270
But sometimes it still hurt her deeply.

00:08:45.950 --> 00:08:47.750
Where did you go instead of practicing?

00:08:50.120 --> 00:08:51.160
Just went around.

00:08:53.510 --> 00:08:54.350
Come here.

00:08:56.160 --> 00:08:57.160
Come here. Come on.

00:08:57.750 --> 00:08:59.240
Step forward. I won't bite.

00:09:03.240 --> 00:09:04.310
Want some?

00:09:09.360 --> 00:09:11.680
Don't you want to go to Chang'an?

00:09:12.920 --> 00:09:13.830
What's this?

00:09:15.390 --> 00:09:16.480
With this,

00:09:17.950 --> 00:09:19.360
forget about Chang'an.

00:09:19.360 --> 00:09:21.390
Even to Antarctica,

00:09:22.390 --> 00:09:23.430
or Africa,

00:09:25.630 --> 00:09:29.430
or the heart of the girl you like.

00:09:30.310 --> 00:09:31.800
You can go instantly.

00:09:32.630 --> 00:09:34.120
Anywhere you want.

00:09:34.920 --> 00:09:35.760
Here.

00:09:38.000 --> 00:09:39.120
You fool.

00:09:41.000 --> 00:09:42.360
Don't skip work tomorrow.

00:09:42.830 --> 00:09:44.480
Go rest. Go on.

00:10:00.750 --> 00:10:01.750
What?

00:10:01.750 --> 00:10:03.070
Save some for me!

00:10:03.070 --> 00:10:03.910
Save some!

00:10:04.390 --> 00:10:05.600
Save it!

00:10:09.000 --> 00:10:10.720
Think of Chang'an.

00:10:11.750 --> 00:10:13.270
Think of Chang'an.

00:10:13.270 --> 00:10:14.200
Think fast!

00:10:15.510 --> 00:10:16.510
It's all gone.

00:10:19.000 --> 00:10:19.870
Stop playing dumb.

00:10:21.910 --> 00:10:22.910
What are you saying?

00:10:24.200 --> 00:10:25.040
What did you say?

00:10:27.390 --> 00:10:28.390
Little brat.

00:10:30.390 --> 00:10:32.600
Kept saying no, then drank half my bottle.

00:10:39.510 --> 00:10:40.510
He arrived in Chang'an.

00:10:42.030 --> 00:10:42.870
Beautiful.

00:10:43.840 --> 00:10:44.680
Beautiful.

00:10:45.290 --> 00:10:46.150
Beautiful.

00:10:46.150 --> 00:10:50.150
Beautiful, so beautiful!

00:11:09.790 --> 00:11:10.630
Where are you?

00:11:38.080 --> 00:11:38.920
Laidi.

00:11:40.630 --> 00:11:41.470
Laidi?

00:11:41.960 --> 00:11:42.800
Laidi!

00:11:47.960 --> 00:11:49.440
What is it, Uncle?

00:11:51.080 --> 00:11:52.150
Took you forever to open up.

00:11:53.120 --> 00:11:54.280
Didn't Liu Hongbing come see you?

00:11:54.790 --> 00:11:55.630
Uncle!

00:12:09.390 --> 00:12:10.630
Qin'e is up too.

00:12:10.630 --> 00:12:11.490
Hurry!

00:12:11.510 --> 00:12:12.910
Try our Chang'an breakfast.

00:12:13.320 --> 00:12:14.200
Okay, okay.

00:12:14.200 --> 00:12:16.150
Tofu pudding, Youtiao, Jinggao.

00:12:16.150 --> 00:12:17.630
- Got everything.
- Alright, alright.

00:12:18.200 --> 00:12:19.040
And there's more.

00:12:20.240 --> 00:12:21.960
Fresh Tangyougao. I kept it

00:12:21.960 --> 00:12:23.360
warm inside my jacket.

00:12:27.080 --> 00:12:27.920
Have you eaten?

00:12:28.840 --> 00:12:29.680
Not yet.

00:12:31.600 --> 00:12:32.440
Hurry and eat.

00:12:33.080 --> 00:12:33.920
Okay.

00:12:34.240 --> 00:12:35.080
Go back and eat.

00:12:36.440 --> 00:12:37.280
Alright.

00:12:37.600 --> 00:12:38.440
So good.

00:12:38.910 --> 00:12:39.750
Eat up.

00:12:51.440 --> 00:12:52.960
I get annoyed just seeing him.

00:12:52.960 --> 00:12:54.030
I don't know what to do.

00:12:55.240 --> 00:12:56.120
Just eat first.

00:12:58.390 --> 00:12:59.240
I'm not eating it.

00:12:59.750 --> 00:13:01.080
I don't want to owe him any favors.

00:13:02.910 --> 00:13:03.750
I asked around.

00:13:04.120 --> 00:13:06.150
Take Bus 14 outside for five stops,

00:13:06.480 --> 00:13:07.510
for the Provincial Troupe.

00:13:08.910 --> 00:13:10.000
After you eat,

00:13:10.750 --> 00:13:11.670
head to the Troupe.

00:13:12.150 --> 00:13:13.270
Do your rehearsals

00:13:13.270 --> 00:13:14.510
or go find Master Gu.

00:13:14.960 --> 00:13:16.200
Leave him to me.

00:13:20.120 --> 00:13:21.870
Uncle, where are we going?

00:13:22.200 --> 00:13:23.440
We're heading out for a bit.

00:13:23.910 --> 00:13:25.030
To the Provincial Troupe?

00:13:26.030 --> 00:13:26.870
No.

00:13:27.600 --> 00:13:28.440
Then where to?

00:13:28.840 --> 00:13:30.510
Just drive and follow my lead.

00:13:31.600 --> 00:13:32.440
Where's Qin'e?

00:13:32.720 --> 00:13:33.870
Practicing in her room.

00:13:35.670 --> 00:13:36.870
Once we head out,

00:13:36.870 --> 00:13:38.390
you'll drive straight south.

00:13:40.080 --> 00:13:40.920
What?

00:13:42.870 --> 00:13:44.200
Qin'e isn't coming?

00:13:45.120 --> 00:13:46.600
Won't you take my orders?

00:13:46.600 --> 00:13:48.200
I will, I will.

00:13:48.200 --> 00:13:49.390
Alright, get in.

00:13:50.200 --> 00:13:51.720
Head straight south out the gate.

00:13:52.600 --> 00:13:53.630
Isn't Qin'e coming?

00:13:55.200 --> 00:13:56.200
Fine, fine, fine.

00:13:56.480 --> 00:13:57.320
Get in.

00:14:19.600 --> 00:14:20.440
Director Ding.

00:14:21.030 --> 00:14:24.150
Chen, stop listening to the radio.

00:14:24.150 --> 00:14:25.510
Keep an eye on the gate.

00:14:25.510 --> 00:14:26.390
Do your duty.

00:14:27.390 --> 00:14:28.230
One more thing.

00:14:28.600 --> 00:14:30.670
If the new guys ask if the leaders are in,

00:14:31.030 --> 00:14:32.550
tell them we're all out.

00:14:42.960 --> 00:14:44.550
Hello, I'm looking for someone.

00:14:44.550 --> 00:14:46.510
Nobody's here. They're all out.

00:14:49.150 --> 00:14:50.720
I'm looking for Master Gu.

00:14:52.440 --> 00:14:53.670
Master Gu?

00:14:54.270 --> 00:14:56.200
The guy in the coat all day?

00:14:56.200 --> 00:14:58.080
The out-of-town old man putting on airs?

00:14:58.670 --> 00:15:00.270
Walk in and turn left at the end.

00:15:00.270 --> 00:15:02.080
It's right by the felt tent.

00:15:04.000 --> 00:15:04.840
Over there?

00:15:05.750 --> 00:15:06.590
Thank you.

00:15:18.750 --> 00:15:20.200
Didn't the leader give us a

00:15:20.200 --> 00:15:21.320
side room?

00:15:21.720 --> 00:15:23.390
You're not sleeping on the street.

00:15:24.080 --> 00:15:25.150
The leader said

00:15:25.480 --> 00:15:26.550
we'll get a room when one opens up.

00:15:26.550 --> 00:15:27.400
Yeah, right.

00:15:27.410 --> 00:15:28.510
Just listen to your nonsense.

00:15:29.000 --> 00:15:30.360
If there's an empty room,

00:15:30.360 --> 00:15:31.960
before the Troupe even assigns it,

00:15:31.960 --> 00:15:33.390
someone will pry the door open.

00:15:33.390 --> 00:15:34.600
You silly old man.

00:15:34.600 --> 00:15:35.480
Heartless jerk.

00:15:35.480 --> 00:15:36.320
Who are you looking for?

00:15:37.960 --> 00:15:38.800
Qing'e!

00:15:39.390 --> 00:15:40.240
Master!

00:15:40.790 --> 00:15:42.320
Master, look who's here!

00:15:42.790 --> 00:15:43.630
Qing'e is here!

00:15:43.630 --> 00:15:44.470
Master.

00:15:44.630 --> 00:15:45.550
Qing'e.

00:15:46.080 --> 00:15:47.600
Come on in, come on in.

00:15:48.640 --> 00:15:49.480
So great you're here.

00:15:49.480 --> 00:15:51.150
Quick, bring out my good tea.

00:15:51.150 --> 00:15:51.990
Brew some for her.

00:15:53.390 --> 00:15:54.480
This is great, so great.

00:15:54.480 --> 00:15:55.840
Qing'e, sit down.

00:15:56.720 --> 00:15:57.560
Sit, sit.

00:15:57.670 --> 00:15:58.670
When did you arrive?

00:15:58.960 --> 00:15:59.870
Just yesterday.

00:15:59.870 --> 00:16:00.840
Just yesterday?

00:16:00.840 --> 00:16:02.240
Good, good. Sit, sit.

00:16:02.240 --> 00:16:03.080
Sit, sit.

00:16:03.600 --> 00:16:04.600
I'm so glad you came.

00:16:05.120 --> 00:16:06.080
Do you know

00:16:06.080 --> 00:16:07.200
why I called you here?

00:16:08.200 --> 00:16:09.150
To perform?

00:16:10.840 --> 00:16:11.680
Let me tell you.

00:16:13.080 --> 00:16:15.440
This is no ordinary play.

00:16:15.910 --> 00:16:17.600
It's what Gou has been dreaming of.

00:16:17.600 --> 00:16:18.750
"You Xi Hu".

00:16:20.550 --> 00:16:23.080
The Regional Opera Festival is at year-end.

00:16:23.440 --> 00:16:26.360
The province wants a good show for Beijing.

00:16:26.630 --> 00:16:28.000
After much consideration,

00:16:28.000 --> 00:16:30.080
they decided "You Xi Hu" is the best.

00:16:30.480 --> 00:16:32.080
They asked me to be the Director.

00:16:32.510 --> 00:16:34.510
That's why I had to call you over.

00:16:34.510 --> 00:16:36.320
I only feel confident with you here.

00:16:39.910 --> 00:16:41.440
Stop smoking, will you?

00:16:41.870 --> 00:16:43.240
The kid is choking.

00:16:43.240 --> 00:16:44.750
She needs to protect her voice!

00:16:44.750 --> 00:16:46.320
Go chat outside if it's too smoky.

00:16:46.320 --> 00:16:47.160
You...

00:16:47.160 --> 00:16:48.020
It's fine. It's okay.

00:16:48.320 --> 00:16:49.200
I'm fine, Master.

00:16:53.510 --> 00:16:55.320
Did the Troupe Leader tell you anything?

00:16:55.720 --> 00:16:57.080
I haven't seen the Troupe Leader yet.

00:16:57.720 --> 00:16:59.750
Did you see Director Ding,
Deputy Troupe Leader?

00:17:01.720 --> 00:17:02.960
So where are you staying?

00:17:03.440 --> 00:17:06.120
The Troupe has no dorms. I'm on my own.

00:17:06.790 --> 00:17:07.750
That Shan the Cripple.

00:17:08.120 --> 00:17:09.390
He promised me!

00:17:09.910 --> 00:17:11.030
Let's go to the General Affairs Section.

00:17:12.120 --> 00:17:13.630
- Don't forget the bed board!
- Let's go.

00:17:13.960 --> 00:17:15.240
Let's go. Go.

00:17:15.360 --> 00:17:17.010
Qing'e, let's go find the Troupe Leader.

00:17:17.030 --> 00:17:17.960
Grab my coat.

00:17:20.270 --> 00:17:21.600
Just look at him.

00:17:22.240 --> 00:17:24.390
Always so eager to help others.

00:17:26.240 --> 00:17:27.080
Section Chief Wang.

00:17:29.720 --> 00:17:31.030
Why are you here again?

00:17:33.030 --> 00:17:34.120
I told you many times.

00:17:34.120 --> 00:17:36.080
No bed boards. No bed boards!

00:17:36.600 --> 00:17:37.960
Even the wooden boards here

00:17:37.960 --> 00:17:39.390
are all strictly accounted for.

00:17:39.390 --> 00:17:40.550
If you take an extra one,

00:17:40.550 --> 00:17:42.270
I'll have to dismantle my own bed for you.

00:17:42.270 --> 00:17:43.440
I'm not here for the board.

00:17:43.440 --> 00:17:44.280
Then what?

00:17:44.840 --> 00:17:45.960
Did the Troupe Leader tell you?

00:17:46.240 --> 00:17:48.480
The empty side room next to mine is

00:17:48.480 --> 00:17:50.120
the new comrade's dorm room now.

00:17:50.120 --> 00:17:51.670
- No.
- Impossible.

00:17:51.790 --> 00:17:53.120
Troupe Leader Shan promised me himself.

00:17:53.360 --> 00:17:54.840
Why would I lie to you?

00:17:54.840 --> 00:17:57.080
Only lead actors get assigned housing.

00:17:57.480 --> 00:17:58.870
Why should a newcomer

00:17:58.870 --> 00:17:59.960
get a dorm room?

00:17:59.960 --> 00:18:01.480
He specially approved it!

00:18:01.790 --> 00:18:03.270
Then go talk to him about it.

00:18:03.270 --> 00:18:04.110
Where is he?

00:18:04.270 --> 00:18:05.360
He's out for a meeting.

00:18:05.960 --> 00:18:06.800
How about this?

00:18:06.960 --> 00:18:08.000
Give me the key first.

00:18:08.060 --> 00:18:08.910
When he gets back,

00:18:08.910 --> 00:18:10.510
I'll have him tell you himself, okay?

00:18:10.510 --> 00:18:12.480
Come on, I'll get the bed board for you.

00:18:13.480 --> 00:18:14.320
Let's go.

00:18:15.390 --> 00:18:16.390
Just a tiny Section Chief.

00:18:16.390 --> 00:18:18.200
Letting power go to your head, huh?

00:18:18.510 --> 00:18:19.390
You just wait.

00:18:19.390 --> 00:18:20.360
I'm going to your boss!

00:18:20.720 --> 00:18:21.600
Go complain to whoever.

00:18:23.150 --> 00:18:24.960
Master, let me find my own place.

00:18:24.960 --> 00:18:25.800
Don't worry about it.

00:18:28.320 --> 00:18:29.360
Where on earth are they?

00:18:30.240 --> 00:18:32.000
All having a crappy meeting?

00:18:32.360 --> 00:18:33.200
I see you!

00:18:33.200 --> 00:18:34.790
- Master, someone's here!
- Who?

00:18:34.790 --> 00:18:36.120
- Someone's inside, look!
- Who?

00:18:36.120 --> 00:18:36.960
I see a shadow.

00:18:37.240 --> 00:18:38.080
Open the door!

00:18:38.750 --> 00:18:40.440
Open up! I see you!

00:18:40.440 --> 00:18:41.280
Open the door!

00:18:41.830 --> 00:18:42.670
Who is it?

00:18:42.720 --> 00:18:43.880
Master, right inside.

00:18:43.880 --> 00:18:45.110
- Master, stop looking.
- You can't hide!

00:18:46.440 --> 00:18:48.030
Don't worry. I brought you here.

00:18:48.030 --> 00:18:49.000
I must properly arrange.

00:18:49.400 --> 00:18:50.790
The cast list for You Xi Hu.

00:18:51.070 --> 00:18:52.240
Don't just watch, come help.

00:18:55.550 --> 00:18:57.200
Help me tear this.

00:18:57.200 --> 00:18:58.040
Okay.

00:18:59.220 --> 00:19:00.070
Is Li Huiniang

00:19:00.070 --> 00:19:00.920
played by so many people?

00:19:02.200 --> 00:19:05.110
One, two, three, four.

00:19:05.110 --> 00:19:07.780
(Yi Qin'e as Role F)

00:19:07.790 --> 00:19:09.680
Master, the sixth one...

00:19:36.400 --> 00:19:37.240
Excuse me,

00:19:38.000 --> 00:19:38.840
can I ask you something?

00:19:39.270 --> 00:19:41.160
There used to be a Factory 618 here,

00:19:41.160 --> 00:19:43.590
later renamed Zhongnan Food Factory.

00:19:43.590 --> 00:19:44.440
Is it here?

00:19:44.440 --> 00:19:46.310
You mean Zhongnan Food Factory?

00:19:46.310 --> 00:19:47.400
You see this?

00:19:47.400 --> 00:19:48.680
This whole area was part of it.

00:19:48.680 --> 00:19:50.920
They moved. It's been empty for a while.

00:19:51.350 --> 00:19:52.200
They moved?

00:20:05.510 --> 00:20:06.350
Why are you laughing?

00:20:11.030 --> 00:20:12.440
Such a huge factory,

00:20:13.680 --> 00:20:15.510
abandoned just like that.

00:20:19.790 --> 00:20:20.630
Hey, brother.

00:20:21.110 --> 00:20:22.110
Why are you here?

00:20:22.830 --> 00:20:24.350
I go wherever it takes me.

00:20:24.880 --> 00:20:25.920
This stubborn donkey

00:20:25.920 --> 00:20:27.400
only grazes right here.

00:20:27.790 --> 00:20:30.160
So I have to come here every day.

00:20:31.830 --> 00:20:33.440
Did you work here too?

00:20:33.440 --> 00:20:34.350
You could say that.

00:20:34.350 --> 00:20:36.110
I used to be the gatekeeper.

00:20:36.790 --> 00:20:39.160
Zhang Guangrong and Hua Caixiang,

00:20:39.160 --> 00:20:40.000
do you know the couple?

00:20:40.310 --> 00:20:41.790
Zhang Guangrong?

00:20:43.680 --> 00:20:44.680
Rings a bell.

00:20:45.030 --> 00:20:46.750
They had a boy with them.

00:20:47.240 --> 00:20:48.790
Where did they move to?

00:20:48.790 --> 00:20:50.160
I don't know.

00:20:50.750 --> 00:20:54.110
The folks came from all over.

00:20:54.590 --> 00:20:56.000
The factory's closed. Everyone's gone.

00:21:28.920 --> 00:21:29.760
Let's go.

00:21:32.550 --> 00:21:33.390
Uncle.

00:21:34.440 --> 00:21:35.400
The person you're looking for...

00:21:35.920 --> 00:21:36.760
Lost.

00:21:38.640 --> 00:21:39.590
Let me help you.

00:21:40.400 --> 00:21:42.200
There's no one Liu Hongbing can't find.

00:21:43.000 --> 00:21:44.070
Why gave me that look?

00:21:44.070 --> 00:21:45.200
I've got connections.

00:21:47.510 --> 00:21:48.350
Move aside!

00:21:58.880 --> 00:21:59.790
Stop hitting him!

00:21:59.790 --> 00:22:00.630
You'll beat him to death!

00:22:02.000 --> 00:22:02.840
Don't run!

00:22:05.880 --> 00:22:06.720
Stop there!

00:22:07.160 --> 00:22:08.000
Run!

00:22:08.880 --> 00:22:09.720
Oh my gosh!

00:22:12.270 --> 00:22:13.110
Are you okay?

00:22:13.510 --> 00:22:15.240
My neck... I can't move my neck.

00:22:15.240 --> 00:22:16.080
What's wrong?

00:22:16.880 --> 00:22:18.350
Don't move. Come on.

00:22:18.350 --> 00:22:19.200
- What are you doing?
- Don't move.

00:22:19.200 --> 00:22:20.560
Who are you? What are you doing?

00:22:23.110 --> 00:22:23.950
Okay.

00:22:24.240 --> 00:22:25.080
How's that?

00:22:25.080 --> 00:22:25.920
So?

00:22:27.680 --> 00:22:28.520
Okay now.

00:22:29.920 --> 00:22:30.760
Not bad.

00:22:32.000 --> 00:22:32.840
Buddy.

00:22:33.070 --> 00:22:34.720
You've got some real skills.

00:22:34.720 --> 00:22:35.560
Who do you run with?

00:22:35.830 --> 00:22:37.160
Get checked at a hospital.

00:22:37.160 --> 00:22:38.440
In case of internal injuries.

00:22:39.000 --> 00:22:40.110
I'm fine. I'm fine.

00:22:40.480 --> 00:22:41.320
Lifesaver.

00:22:41.590 --> 00:22:43.030
Thanks for your help.

00:22:43.640 --> 00:22:45.270
I'm Diao Laohei from Diaojia Village.

00:22:45.680 --> 00:22:46.550
See you around.

00:22:49.350 --> 00:22:50.350
Stop running!

00:22:51.780 --> 00:22:52.640
Where is he off to now?

00:22:52.640 --> 00:22:53.510
What's going on?

00:22:56.640 --> 00:22:57.590
He's fighting again?

00:22:58.160 --> 00:22:59.350
Should've just left him alone.

00:23:03.830 --> 00:23:04.670
This...

00:23:06.110 --> 00:23:07.000
Look at this mess.

00:23:09.110 --> 00:23:10.400
Where'd you learn to do that?

00:23:10.720 --> 00:23:11.560
Hurry and eat.

00:23:11.830 --> 00:23:12.790
Then in a bit,

00:23:13.240 --> 00:23:15.030
we'll hit a bathhouse for a scrub.

00:23:15.640 --> 00:23:18.200
Chang'an has great bathhouses.

00:23:20.400 --> 00:23:21.240
What?

00:23:21.590 --> 00:23:22.510
Feeling unwell anywhere?

00:23:22.510 --> 00:23:23.350
I can fix it for you.

00:23:23.750 --> 00:23:24.590
No, thanks.

00:23:24.840 --> 00:23:25.680
I feel fine.

00:23:25.680 --> 00:23:26.520
Tear the buns.

00:23:32.590 --> 00:23:33.960
This won't work, Master.

00:23:34.400 --> 00:23:35.880
I'll just give up the house.

00:23:36.510 --> 00:23:38.200
What are you doing? Stop!

00:23:38.720 --> 00:23:39.640
Director Ding is here.

00:23:41.750 --> 00:23:43.790
Gu, what are you doing?

00:23:44.590 --> 00:23:45.920
I couldn't stop him.

00:23:46.310 --> 00:23:48.270
My apprentice bumped his head as a kid.

00:23:48.640 --> 00:23:50.030
He hates being stopped.

00:23:50.880 --> 00:23:52.590
He'd smash a lock if it got in his way,

00:23:52.590 --> 00:23:53.430
let alone a person.

00:23:53.680 --> 00:23:55.960
Situan, let's just drop it.

00:23:58.640 --> 00:23:59.480
Stop!

00:24:01.480 --> 00:24:02.350
See?

00:24:02.350 --> 00:24:03.750
There's no stopping him.

00:24:04.030 --> 00:24:05.000
Gu.

00:24:05.480 --> 00:24:06.720
The Troupe is tight on housing.

00:24:06.790 --> 00:24:08.790
We can't provide housing for new comrades.

00:24:09.200 --> 00:24:10.550
No exceptions for anyone.

00:24:10.550 --> 00:24:11.400
Is that so?

00:24:13.920 --> 00:24:15.200
I saw that. You smashed it.

00:24:15.200 --> 00:24:16.040
Director Ding.

00:24:16.550 --> 00:24:18.590
Don't go near. It's dangerous.

00:24:23.720 --> 00:24:24.590
But...

00:24:26.510 --> 00:24:27.880
for comrades who are truly in need,

00:24:27.880 --> 00:24:29.720
we won't just ignore them.

00:24:30.350 --> 00:24:31.270
We operate on

00:24:31.270 --> 00:24:33.240
the principle of serving the people.

00:24:33.550 --> 00:24:35.440
We must follow procedures for everything.

00:24:35.880 --> 00:24:37.720
It has to follow the rules, right?

00:24:38.880 --> 00:24:39.720
This matter

00:24:40.070 --> 00:24:41.640
completely follows the rules.

00:24:42.200 --> 00:24:44.270
Troupe Leader Shan promised me himself.

00:24:44.720 --> 00:24:45.750
But he's not here right now.

00:24:46.830 --> 00:24:47.920
She's already here.

00:24:47.920 --> 00:24:50.030
I can't let her sleep on the street.

00:24:50.640 --> 00:24:52.880
So I had to make the call myself.

00:24:53.270 --> 00:24:55.310
If you don't believe me, just ask.

00:24:57.480 --> 00:24:59.480
Understood. Understood!

00:24:59.480 --> 00:25:00.920
I'm here now, aren't I?

00:25:01.790 --> 00:25:04.030
Wang, give the newcomer the keys.

00:25:06.110 --> 00:25:07.200
Still necessary?

00:25:14.240 --> 00:25:16.440
You must be the newcomer from Ningzhou.

00:25:16.440 --> 00:25:17.280
Welcome, welcome.

00:25:17.290 --> 00:25:18.240
Yi Qin'e.

00:25:19.440 --> 00:25:21.960
Deputy leader of Ningzhou County Troupe.

00:25:22.680 --> 00:25:23.520
Qin'e.

00:25:23.880 --> 00:25:26.960
This is Director Ding, Performance Section.

00:25:27.680 --> 00:25:28.790
If you need anything,

00:25:28.790 --> 00:25:30.720
just trouble Director Ding.

00:25:30.720 --> 00:25:31.880
Don't shoulder it all yourself.

00:25:31.880 --> 00:25:32.740
No, no.

00:25:32.750 --> 00:25:34.680
It's no trouble at all.

00:25:35.240 --> 00:25:36.510
It's just bad timing.

00:25:36.830 --> 00:25:38.880
Troupe Leader, deputies, and key staff

00:25:38.880 --> 00:25:40.030
are all out on business.

00:25:40.400 --> 00:25:42.790
So I'm handling everything here.

00:25:43.510 --> 00:25:44.830
We'll find time later

00:25:44.830 --> 00:25:47.400
to have a proper talk, alright?

00:25:47.960 --> 00:25:49.590
I'll get back to work.

00:25:53.920 --> 00:25:56.200
Wang, pick up the lock.

00:26:03.510 --> 00:26:04.350
Situan,

00:26:05.270 --> 00:26:07.070
hurry up and tidy the room.

00:26:09.200 --> 00:26:10.480
Just settle in for now.

00:26:10.920 --> 00:26:12.070
Don't worry about a thing.

00:26:12.070 --> 00:26:12.910
I've got you.

00:26:13.440 --> 00:26:14.640
What belongs to us,

00:26:15.070 --> 00:26:15.910
slowly,

00:26:16.350 --> 00:26:17.190
we'll get it all back.

00:26:21.270 --> 00:26:22.590
The show is over.

00:26:22.590 --> 00:26:23.510
Go back.

00:26:23.510 --> 00:26:30.510
(Saving water is everyone's duty)

00:26:43.420 --> 00:26:46.660
(Stay Clean; Bathhouse)

00:26:46.660 --> 00:26:49.900
(Welcome to People's Bathhouse)

00:26:57.160 --> 00:26:58.590
Did I lose him when taking a bath?

00:27:23.920 --> 00:27:24.760
Hongbing.

00:27:33.480 --> 00:27:34.320
Where's she?

00:27:34.590 --> 00:27:35.480
She checked out.

00:27:35.920 --> 00:27:36.880
Checked out?

00:27:37.640 --> 00:27:38.480
Where did she go?

00:27:38.720 --> 00:27:39.590
I don't know.

00:27:39.590 --> 00:27:41.550
I think her company assigned her a place.

00:27:41.960 --> 00:27:42.830
What?

00:27:46.200 --> 00:27:47.310
What the heck?

00:27:48.750 --> 00:27:50.000
Hongbing, where are you going?

00:27:50.310 --> 00:27:51.160
None of your business.

00:27:51.160 --> 00:27:52.000
Go, go, go.

00:27:53.680 --> 00:27:57.440
Look. A, B, C, D, E, F.

00:27:58.110 --> 00:27:59.440
It's already down to F.

00:27:59.960 --> 00:28:01.510
Some star? What star?

00:28:01.960 --> 00:28:03.550
She's just an extra.

00:28:05.480 --> 00:28:07.750
All the top Qinqiang Opera singers

00:28:07.750 --> 00:28:08.590
are gathered right here.

00:28:08.920 --> 00:28:11.160
She's now a hen surrounded by phoenixes.

00:28:11.750 --> 00:28:12.720
Let me tell you.

00:28:13.790 --> 00:28:16.350
Our Qin'e is the real phoenix.

00:28:17.160 --> 00:28:19.680
Do you know her biggest strength?

00:28:20.550 --> 00:28:21.390
Being blunt!

00:28:22.790 --> 00:28:25.350
An unassuming look hides a sharp edge.

00:28:26.480 --> 00:28:29.830
Appear harmless outside, stay sharp inside.

00:28:29.830 --> 00:28:31.270
That's her exactly.

00:28:33.160 --> 00:28:34.590
I've got it all figured out.

00:28:35.790 --> 00:28:38.680
Her skills are a part of her and no one

00:28:38.680 --> 00:28:39.830
can take them away.

00:28:40.830 --> 00:28:42.550
We have nothing to fear.

00:28:44.590 --> 00:28:47.110
You old fox, you're so sly.

00:28:50.030 --> 00:28:51.510
Enough about me, what about you?

00:28:51.510 --> 00:28:52.400
What are your plans?

00:28:53.720 --> 00:28:54.560
Stay in Chang'an.

00:28:55.960 --> 00:28:58.960
I'm like bricks from a torn-down house.

00:28:58.960 --> 00:29:00.030
Useless no matter where I go.

00:29:01.400 --> 00:29:03.680
Broken or not, Qin bricks and Han tiles

00:29:04.160 --> 00:29:06.960
are still valuable in Chang'an.

00:29:08.830 --> 00:29:09.830
Let's be serious.

00:29:10.350 --> 00:29:14.070
If you play the drums for us,

00:29:14.550 --> 00:29:16.750
I'll feel much more confident.

00:29:18.400 --> 00:29:21.070
Let's win this battle for Qin'e first.

00:29:21.750 --> 00:29:23.640
Don't worry, I've got her back.

00:29:24.590 --> 00:29:26.480
Situan, how's the food?

00:29:27.160 --> 00:29:28.160
Situan is back?

00:29:29.070 --> 00:29:30.400
I had no choice.

00:29:30.920 --> 00:29:32.590
Though he's my relative's only boy,

00:29:32.920 --> 00:29:33.960
I had to bring him out here.

00:29:34.990 --> 00:29:35.830
Right.

00:29:35.830 --> 00:29:37.550
How did you find a wife?

00:29:38.790 --> 00:29:39.960
We divorced long ago.

00:29:40.510 --> 00:29:42.790
After we got famous in Beishan,

00:29:43.310 --> 00:29:44.510
she found me and said

00:29:45.030 --> 00:29:46.400
she had nowhere else to go.

00:29:46.400 --> 00:29:47.480
I felt bad for her.

00:29:47.920 --> 00:29:49.480
So we made do living together.

00:29:51.510 --> 00:29:52.640
Master, you called for me?

00:29:53.110 --> 00:29:54.030
Where's the Mo?

00:29:54.590 --> 00:29:56.720
She said there's no Mo, only words.

00:29:57.550 --> 00:29:58.440
What words?

00:29:58.440 --> 00:29:59.280
She said this.

00:29:59.750 --> 00:30:00.590
No food!

00:30:00.590 --> 00:30:02.030
Your master is a fool!

00:30:02.510 --> 00:30:04.240
All he does every day is rehearse.

00:30:04.240 --> 00:30:05.350
He won't even light the stove!

00:30:05.350 --> 00:30:06.960
Let the old geezer freeze to death!

00:30:07.270 --> 00:30:08.310
That's exactly what she said.

00:30:10.400 --> 00:30:11.480
Blockhead, get lost!

00:30:14.400 --> 00:30:16.790
She's great. What a personality.

00:30:16.790 --> 00:30:18.160
See why we got divorced?

00:30:36.350 --> 00:30:37.640
How did you find this place?

00:30:38.880 --> 00:30:40.550
Is this the place they gave you?

00:30:42.350 --> 00:30:43.510
There's nothing here.

00:30:44.790 --> 00:30:45.750
Come on, let's go.

00:30:45.750 --> 00:30:47.310
Put it down. Come back with me.

00:30:47.750 --> 00:30:49.200
- Let's go.
- Stop pulling me!

00:30:49.200 --> 00:30:50.050
I'm not going!

00:30:50.110 --> 00:30:51.160
You can't stay here.

00:30:51.550 --> 00:30:52.640
Just look at this place.

00:30:52.640 --> 00:30:53.720
It's completely unlivable.

00:30:53.720 --> 00:30:54.560
What's going on?

00:30:56.070 --> 00:30:56.910
Uncle Sanyuan.

00:30:57.240 --> 00:30:58.270
How did you find this place?

00:30:58.790 --> 00:31:00.160
Look at this place.

00:31:00.160 --> 00:31:02.000
It's not fit for humans.

00:31:02.000 --> 00:31:02.840
Go, go.

00:31:03.830 --> 00:31:05.160
Watch what you say.

00:31:05.720 --> 00:31:06.590
Do the people living here

00:31:06.590 --> 00:31:07.790
not look human to you?

00:31:08.680 --> 00:31:09.520
Right, right.

00:31:10.160 --> 00:31:11.030
I'll rephrase that.

00:31:11.880 --> 00:31:13.590
You don't have to stay at the guesthouse.

00:31:13.590 --> 00:31:15.310
My buddy has an apartment in Duanlyumen.

00:31:15.310 --> 00:31:16.640
It's very close to here.

00:31:16.640 --> 00:31:18.070
It even has an indoor bathroom.

00:31:18.070 --> 00:31:19.240
Mountain folks are used to hardship.

00:31:19.510 --> 00:31:20.920
We like it here just fine.

00:31:21.160 --> 00:31:22.830
Stop worrying and just go. Go.

00:31:22.830 --> 00:31:24.200
Without a decent place to live,

00:31:24.200 --> 00:31:25.270
how can she put on a good show?

00:31:25.270 --> 00:31:26.590
Just leave! Go!

00:31:27.030 --> 00:31:29.400
Uncle, let me know if she wants to move.

00:31:29.400 --> 00:31:30.240
No big deal.

00:31:30.830 --> 00:31:31.670
No need.

00:31:32.550 --> 00:31:33.880
I'll see myself out.

00:31:33.880 --> 00:31:34.920
His skin is thicker than

00:31:35.510 --> 00:31:36.640
the city wall.

00:31:37.200 --> 00:31:38.310
What a pain...

00:31:40.200 --> 00:31:41.310
What if he comes back?

00:31:46.510 --> 00:31:47.350
Keep the door locked.

00:31:48.030 --> 00:31:49.870
Draw a line. He's not allowed in.

00:31:49.870 --> 00:31:50.750
Talking nonsense?

00:31:50.750 --> 00:31:51.790
"Shut up."

00:31:51.790 --> 00:31:52.790
Pestering you?

00:31:52.790 --> 00:31:53.640
"Get lost."

00:31:54.030 --> 00:31:55.070
Use those moves.

00:31:55.070 --> 00:31:56.400
Hit him hard with them.

00:31:56.400 --> 00:31:57.680
I bet that'll scare him off.

00:31:58.070 --> 00:31:59.310
I don't think he's scared.

00:32:14.310 --> 00:32:15.240
You're grown up now.

00:32:15.240 --> 00:32:16.830
Guys will naturally chase you.

00:32:17.720 --> 00:32:19.200
You need to learn to say no.

00:32:24.160 --> 00:32:25.310
Do you remember Aunt Hua?

00:32:26.070 --> 00:32:26.920
Learn from her.

00:32:27.790 --> 00:32:30.200
She'd yell and scratch right away.

00:32:30.200 --> 00:32:32.310
She'd rip their mouths for talking nonsense.

00:32:33.750 --> 00:32:35.480
Aunt Hua did scold you before.

00:32:36.200 --> 00:32:38.000
But you never pursued her.

00:32:40.030 --> 00:32:42.310
I said learn from her. Why bring me up?

00:32:57.070 --> 00:32:59.240
I wonder what she is doing now.

00:33:06.790 --> 00:33:08.030
Where are you going?

00:33:08.590 --> 00:33:10.350
Just crash at my place for the night.

00:33:11.110 --> 00:33:12.030
Don't worry about me.

00:33:12.400 --> 00:33:13.720
I have plenty of places to go.

00:33:15.240 --> 00:33:16.720
Just take care of yourself.

00:33:20.000 --> 00:33:21.400
I'll go say goodbye to your master.

00:33:23.920 --> 00:33:25.070
Can't you stop smoking?

00:33:25.510 --> 00:33:26.680
You're choking everyone.

00:33:27.240 --> 00:33:28.270
What are you even practicing?

00:33:28.790 --> 00:33:30.440
Look at your wrinkled face.

00:33:30.440 --> 00:33:31.960
- Don't listen.
- Think you belong on stage?

00:33:31.960 --> 00:33:33.590
Let's go, Uncle. Don't listen.

00:33:33.590 --> 00:33:34.790
What else would I do but smoke?

00:33:36.510 --> 00:33:37.680
Your master has changed too.

00:33:38.240 --> 00:33:39.640
He doesn't dare to talk back.

00:33:40.160 --> 00:33:41.960
Forget it. Let's not interrupt them.

00:33:43.640 --> 00:33:44.880
Everything changes.

00:33:45.590 --> 00:33:47.550
But once you master the skills,

00:33:47.550 --> 00:33:48.510
they will never change.

00:33:49.110 --> 00:33:50.590
Just like I said...

00:33:50.590 --> 00:33:52.000
I know what I have to do.

00:34:06.070 --> 00:34:06.910
Sir.

00:34:07.480 --> 00:34:09.070
People can't just walk in here, right?

00:34:09.590 --> 00:34:10.430
Of course not.

00:34:11.440 --> 00:34:12.830
Keep an eye on that guy at the door.

00:34:12.830 --> 00:34:13.670
Don't let him in.

00:34:14.560 --> 00:34:15.400
Who?

00:34:15.400 --> 00:34:16.240
That guy.

00:34:23.590 --> 00:34:24.440
Why haven't you left yet?

00:34:24.440 --> 00:34:25.280
What are you doing here?

00:34:25.680 --> 00:34:26.520
Waiting for you.

00:34:26.750 --> 00:34:27.590
Why wait for me?

00:34:27.920 --> 00:34:29.640
Qin'e has a place to stay, but you don't.

00:34:29.640 --> 00:34:30.720
Let's head back.

00:34:31.720 --> 00:34:33.200
Since when do I need you?

00:34:33.830 --> 00:34:34.670
Uncle.

00:34:35.550 --> 00:34:38.640
There's a killer in Chang'an, Wei Zhenhai.

00:34:38.640 --> 00:34:40.270
He has a gun and is very dangerous.

00:34:42.720 --> 00:34:44.590
Can you relax if we don't live together?

00:34:44.960 --> 00:34:45.920
Aren't you afraid I'll

00:34:45.920 --> 00:34:47.590
sneak over late and bother Qin'e?

00:34:48.200 --> 00:34:49.270
You little brat!

00:34:49.270 --> 00:34:50.110
Uncle.

00:34:50.270 --> 00:34:51.640
The way you snore

00:34:51.640 --> 00:34:53.400
sounds just like my dad.

00:34:53.400 --> 00:34:55.270
It puts my mind at ease.

00:34:56.510 --> 00:34:57.350
Come on.

00:34:57.700 --> 00:34:58.550
Let's go.

00:34:58.550 --> 00:34:59.390
What are you doing?

00:35:00.070 --> 00:35:01.070
Let's head back.

00:35:01.070 --> 00:35:01.910
Let's go.

00:35:13.200 --> 00:35:14.040
Listen.

00:35:16.310 --> 00:35:18.070
The rent for this room.

00:35:18.070 --> 00:35:19.160
We'll split it evenly.

00:35:19.790 --> 00:35:21.680
Uncle, why are you doing this?

00:35:21.680 --> 00:35:22.880
A slap in the face?

00:35:22.880 --> 00:35:23.750
Fine, you win.

00:35:24.350 --> 00:35:25.270
Have it your way.

00:35:26.480 --> 00:35:28.640
I'll find a place to stay soon

00:35:29.110 --> 00:35:30.030
and move out.

00:35:30.880 --> 00:35:31.720
Uncle.

00:35:32.110 --> 00:35:33.200
What are you doing?

00:35:34.160 --> 00:35:35.550
You're so defensive with me.

00:35:36.070 --> 00:35:37.880
I truly care about Qin'e.

00:35:39.400 --> 00:35:40.240
I swear.

00:35:40.480 --> 00:35:41.790
The first time I saw Qin'e,

00:35:41.790 --> 00:35:43.920
I knew what I'd be like in 40 years.

00:35:45.070 --> 00:35:46.030
Be like what?

00:35:46.710 --> 00:35:47.880
You idiot.

00:35:48.550 --> 00:35:51.030
Her priority now is singing well.

00:35:51.030 --> 00:35:51.880
Got it?

00:35:51.880 --> 00:35:52.960
I know.

00:35:53.440 --> 00:35:55.190
I love her singing too.

00:35:55.190 --> 00:35:56.400
I won't get in her way.

00:35:56.400 --> 00:35:57.480
You're so shameless.

00:35:57.480 --> 00:35:58.320
You...

00:36:02.160 --> 00:36:03.570
Listen to me, kid.

00:36:04.190 --> 00:36:05.710
In this line of work,

00:36:06.030 --> 00:36:07.230
when actors take the stage,

00:36:07.710 --> 00:36:09.710
most of the crowd just likes

00:36:09.710 --> 00:36:11.800
their pretty painted faces.

00:36:12.800 --> 00:36:15.190
Looks will fade sooner or later.

00:36:15.880 --> 00:36:17.670
Strip the skin and the flesh inside...

00:36:18.150 --> 00:36:19.760
Few people would actually want.

00:36:22.800 --> 00:36:23.920
But with Qin'e,

00:36:24.800 --> 00:36:25.840
forget the flesh,

00:36:26.440 --> 00:36:27.710
I'd even take the nuts.

00:36:28.190 --> 00:36:29.880
You're the one who's nuts!

00:36:31.150 --> 00:36:32.710
Uncle, why are you mad?

00:36:33.030 --> 00:36:34.000
I'm not staying here.

00:36:34.000 --> 00:36:34.840
I'm leaving!

00:36:35.280 --> 00:36:36.510
- Uncle, don't!
- So mad!

00:36:36.710 --> 00:36:37.610
- Please stay.
- Let go!

00:36:39.000 --> 00:36:40.070
Bring me the towel!

00:36:46.480 --> 00:36:47.320
Here.

00:37:18.190 --> 00:37:19.030
Xiaoxiao?

00:37:20.880 --> 00:37:21.720
Xiaoxiao.

00:37:24.800 --> 00:37:25.760
Xiaoxiao.

00:37:33.710 --> 00:37:34.920
Xiaoxiao, it's me!

00:37:36.480 --> 00:37:37.400
It's Laidi!

00:37:37.760 --> 00:37:38.710
Xiaoxiao!

00:37:39.550 --> 00:37:40.390
Xiaoxiao!

00:39:49.920 --> 00:39:51.800
The woody scent of the barre,

00:39:51.800 --> 00:39:53.760
the smell of sweat on the carpet,

00:39:54.440 --> 00:39:57.400
mixed with the dust of old costumes,

00:39:57.400 --> 00:39:59.150
all wash over her at once.

00:39:59.880 --> 00:40:01.840
Yi Qin'e feels grounded.

00:40:02.800 --> 00:40:05.030
It's the scent she knows best.

00:40:05.590 --> 00:40:08.360
Once she starts training and rehearsing,

00:40:09.030 --> 00:40:10.920
she can leave

00:40:10.920 --> 00:40:13.510
all her troubles behind.

00:40:15.480 --> 00:40:17.550
Master Gou once summarized her.

00:40:18.230 --> 00:40:19.550
Hardworking.

00:40:19.550 --> 00:40:20.760
Slow to grasp.

00:40:20.760 --> 00:40:22.190
Slow to get into character.

00:40:22.880 --> 00:40:23.920
Later,

00:40:23.920 --> 00:40:25.550
he added a few more traits.

00:40:26.550 --> 00:40:27.510
Good memory.

00:40:28.280 --> 00:40:29.920
Diligent practice.

00:40:29.920 --> 00:40:31.440
Solid acting.

00:40:32.150 --> 00:40:34.000
Learning through sheer hard work

00:40:34.760 --> 00:40:36.760
is her only way out.

00:40:36.760 --> 00:40:41.180
(Innovate)

00:41:22.280 --> 00:41:25.110
Why clean the rehearsal hall at all?

00:41:25.110 --> 00:41:26.630
Why are we so unlucky?

00:41:26.630 --> 00:41:27.630
You have the nerve to say that?

00:41:27.960 --> 00:41:29.590
You got caught 'cause you're slow.

00:41:30.280 --> 00:41:31.120
Hurry up.

00:41:31.480 --> 00:41:33.070
While they're still asleep,

00:41:33.400 --> 00:41:34.800
we can still go back to sleep.

00:41:49.920 --> 00:41:50.880
Who's she?

00:41:51.110 --> 00:41:52.320
Shh, be quiet.

00:42:07.150 --> 00:42:08.110
Zhou Yuzhi.

00:42:08.760 --> 00:42:10.190
Hurry and practice, stop doing your makeup.

00:42:11.320 --> 00:42:12.670
I'm not you.

00:42:13.190 --> 00:42:14.480
Why bother practicing?

00:42:14.480 --> 00:42:16.150
I'll still be an extra anyway.

00:42:18.230 --> 00:42:23.920
♪Old Yang Ye weeps tears of blood♪

00:42:28.280 --> 00:42:35.480
♪Head bowed, cursing the heavens♪

00:42:35.710 --> 00:42:44.400
♪Since Pan Renmei was born♪

00:42:44.400 --> 00:42:46.590
♪There shouldn't♪

00:42:52.510 --> 00:42:54.150
Why's everyone so active today?

00:42:57.360 --> 00:42:58.920
Looks like our classmate.

00:42:59.710 --> 00:43:00.630
Yi Qing'e!

00:43:01.230 --> 00:43:02.440
Yi Qing'e!

00:43:02.440 --> 00:43:03.670
It really is you!

00:43:05.020 --> 00:43:06.940
=The Lead=
(Preview)

00:43:09.560 --> 00:43:10.510
Stop.

00:43:11.160 --> 00:43:12.120
Even less than a minute.

00:43:12.360 --> 00:43:14.840
How does this help shape the character?

00:43:14.870 --> 00:43:15.960
Rigid.

00:43:15.960 --> 00:43:16.820
What?

00:43:17.520 --> 00:43:18.960
Actor A sings

00:43:18.960 --> 00:43:20.680
nothing like our county troupe's actors.

00:43:20.760 --> 00:43:21.600
Completely different styles.

00:43:21.760 --> 00:43:23.280
The Provincial Troupe pursues

00:43:23.400 --> 00:43:25.120
a modern, trendy style.

00:43:25.160 --> 00:43:26.840
She's only an extra.

00:43:27.280 --> 00:43:28.480
Why are you worried?

00:43:28.600 --> 00:43:30.000
I won't allow her to steal my chance.

00:43:30.080 --> 00:43:32.080
(Mahjong)
I saw you've got rooms for rent.

00:43:37.000 --> 00:43:41.620
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

00:43:43.090 --> 00:43:47.930
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

00:43:49.370 --> 00:43:53.560
♪We met and brushed past♪

00:43:55.120 --> 00:44:02.420
♪Your shadow drifted out of sight♪

00:44:16.790 --> 00:44:20.540
♪The stove fire blazed in my dream♪

00:44:22.140 --> 00:44:27.710
♪Lit up the tracks of pearly tears♪

00:44:28.830 --> 00:44:32.890
♪In my dream, water sleeves flew♪

00:44:34.020 --> 00:44:39.610
♪Hiding a lifetime of love♪

00:44:40.770 --> 00:44:44.970
♪The Qinling Mountains
crossed the stage♪

00:44:46.010 --> 00:44:51.640
♪Spring water brewed strong wine♪

00:44:52.810 --> 00:44:57.500
♪Sheep moved through the valley♪

00:44:58.180 --> 00:45:03.350
♪It felt like a promise
from another life♪

00:45:04.020 --> 00:45:09.050
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

00:45:10.080 --> 00:45:15.510
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

00:45:15.890 --> 00:45:21.170
♪If I chose again, I'd still roam♪

00:45:22.120 --> 00:45:27.930
♪All over this sunlit plateau♪

00:45:27.930 --> 00:45:33.350
♪The dream ends; the curtain falls♪

00:45:33.900 --> 00:45:39.410
♪Moonlight washes off this stage makeup♪

00:45:39.960 --> 00:45:44.920
♪The one in the mirror wears gray hair♪

00:45:45.940 --> 00:45:51.220
♪Already sang all my joy and sorrow♪

00:45:52.020 --> 00:46:01.050
♪Already shouted across Qinchuan Plain♪